🚀 Exciting Internship Project  🚀

I'm thrilled to share that I've just completed my first task as an intern at Oasis Infobyte, and it has been an incredible learning experience! 🎉



📊 Project Name :-----

 Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on Retail Sales Data



📊 Live Project Link :-----

>https://lnkd.in/d2YRTgqZ



